column3: NSLOCTEXT("", "C0D4EE44413D214DC7469EA2C2EF360A", "We\'re finally here! come on Dusk!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "68D45CB346FE57CD0FC1D8A5D942084E", "Poor Elli. She must have forgotten she can\'t travel in this dream without you.")
NSLOCTEXT("", "AE20C01F43553BB85D35B2BE9EC9FA26", "I\'m sorry Dusk. I should have known better than to run off alone like that.")
